These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different games are played: snooker, go, canasta, chess
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, chestnut, fuchsia, turquise
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, writing, board-games, sudoku
 1. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 3. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 6. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person playing snooker##7
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
12. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | chess    | go | canasta    | snooker   |
| Color   | azure | fuchsia | chestnut | turquise |
| Beverage           | tea       | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate  | milk     |
| Hobby     | woodworking      | board-games   | sudoku    | writing    |

