4 different games are played: chess, canasta, whist, bridge
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, tea, mirinda
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, september, october
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 2. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 3. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 7. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
11. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | goat   | lizard       | fish    | horse      |
