The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, photographer, software-developer, security-guard
House: art-deco, tower, craftsman, palace
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, scooter, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, reggae, punk
 1. the fan punk is the photographer##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the photographer##1
 3. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the software-developer##1
 5. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 6. the fan ambient is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 7. the photographer is somewhere between the fan d&b and the fan ambient##7
 8. the security-guard is not the fan d&b##6
 9. the fan reggae is on the left or right of the fan ambient##3
10. the art-deco house is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
11. the craftsman house is on the right of the tower house##1
12. the photographer is on the left of the fan ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job         | fisherman      | photographer   | security-guard   | software-developer       |
| House   | palace | art-deco    | tower | craftsman       |
| Transport   | boat  | tram | scooter   | jet-ski     |
| Music-Genre         | d&b   | punk    | ambient   | reggae |

