.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, amaryllis, poppy, aconite
House: farmhouse, townhouse, wooden, cottage
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, folk, reggae, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blue, green, ebony
 1. the fan r&b is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
 3. the fan r&b is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes green##2
 4. the fan pop is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the townhouse house is not the person who likes blue##6
 6. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 7. the person who growsaconite is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the cottage house##7
 8. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
10. the townhouse house is on the right of the fan r&b##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is the wooden house##1
12. the wooden house is not the person who likes green##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | aconite     | poppy   | begonia |
| House       | cottage   | farmhouse | townhouse | wooden    |
| Music-Genre      | reggae | r&b | pop   | folk  |
| Color        | ebony | fuchsia     | green   | blue |

