.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, red, blood-red, amber
City: hamburg, edinburgh, hannover, marseilles
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, skateboard, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, australian, argentine, mexican
 1. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
 2. the dutch is between the person traveling to hannover and the person driving the car##2
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the australian is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to hamburg##7
 8. the dutch is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
 9. the person driving the boat is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the dutch##3
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the mexican##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is not the person who likes red##6
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
14. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the dutch##3
15. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
