.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald, grey, red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, documentary, disaster
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, poker, snooker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, old-henry, aristoff, baccarat
 1. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5
 2. the person watching documentary movies is the person who likes grey##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person playing poker is between the person who likes red and the person who likes emerald##2
 5. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
 6. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person who likes apricot##7
 7. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
 8. the person playing scrabble is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
10. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
12. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | red      | grey     | emerald   | apricot    |
| Movie-Genre     | disaster | documentary   | superhero | animation |
| Game     | snooker        | poker     | scrabble  | backgammon      |
| Cigar   | old-henry       | baccarat | prince   | aristoff    |

 